Package org.mozilla.javascript.ast

Interface Summary
DestructuringForm Common interface for ArrayLiteral and ObjectLiteral node types, both of which may appear in "destructuring" expressions or contexts.
IdeErrorReporter This is interface defines a protocol for the reporting of errors during JavaScript translation in IDE-mode.
NodeVisitor Simple visitor interface for traversing the AST.
